WEBVTT

01:27.380 --> 01:31.910
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.180 --> 01:34.910
[Episode 22]

01:35.020 --> 01:38.410
[Sanjie Police Station, Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

04:33.390 --> 04:34.440
Help!

04:50.720 --> 04:51.430
Let go.

04:52.750 --> 04:53.480
Let go.

04:54.030 --> 04:55.750
Let go!

04:56.040 --> 04:57.850
Let go!

04:58.040 --> 04:59.330
You killed Zishan.

04:59.510 --> 05:01.160
I won't let you go.

05:21.390 --> 05:21.920
Mom!

05:22.830 --> 05:23.360
Mom!

05:24.040 --> 05:24.740
Mom!

05:27.240 --> 05:28.050
Mom!

05:28.720 --> 05:29.520
Mom!

05:32.680 --> 05:33.630
Is anyone there?

05:33.630 --> 05:34.270
Mom!

05:34.270 --> 05:35.710
Is anyone over there?

05:36.560 --> 05:38.030
Is anyone over there?

05:39.360 --> 05:40.310
Is anyone there?

05:41.390 --> 05:42.380
Mom!

05:43.270 --> 05:44.960
Is anyone inside?

05:45.680 --> 05:46.960
Is anyone there?

05:47.070 --> 05:48.800
Mom!

05:49.360 --> 05:50.480
Where are you?

05:51.480 --> 05:52.720
-Is anyone there?
-Mom!

05:52.720 --> 05:54.020
Help!

05:57.360 --> 05:58.920
-Mom!
-Help!

05:59.270 --> 06:00.000
Mom!

06:00.270 --> 06:01.000
Mom!

06:02.000 --> 06:02.940
Mom!

06:04.190 --> 06:05.420
Mom!

06:05.560 --> 06:07.160
Mom!

06:09.200 --> 06:10.820
-Help!
-Mom!

06:11.000 --> 06:13.680
-Help!
-Mom!

07:27.510 --> 07:28.570
What are you doing?

07:33.980 --> 07:34.980
How did you get in?

08:00.050 --> 08:01.100
I knew it was you.

08:08.370 --> 08:08.990
Hello.

08:09.230 --> 08:10.830
Your idea is very inspiring.

08:11.100 --> 08:12.800
Instigating Qiao Zishan to kill her mother

08:12.800 --> 08:14.040
shouldn't be the reason that scared Mister

08:14.040 --> 08:15.540
and made him close the Amusement Park.

08:15.540 --> 08:16.000
Yes.

08:16.960 --> 08:18.560
If that were really the case,

08:18.740 --> 08:19.510
he should have proudly

08:19.510 --> 08:21.860
publicized it all over the Amusement Park.

08:21.860 --> 08:23.260
We analyzed this before.

08:23.630 --> 08:25.160
His sudden closure of the Amusement Park

08:25.160 --> 08:27.000
is likely due to some emergency

08:27.000 --> 08:28.730
that made him feel endangered.

08:28.870 --> 08:29.830
I asked a mainland forensic doctor

08:29.830 --> 08:32.620
to carefully review
Qiao Lihua's autopsy report.

08:32.620 --> 08:35.820
He was suspicious about the wound
on the deceased's head.

08:35.870 --> 08:37.789
He thinks it could be a crush injury,

08:37.789 --> 08:40.350
or a blow from a curved blunt object.

08:40.640 --> 08:44.480
Did he really kill someone himself?

08:45.000 --> 08:46.480
It's impossible to tell right now.

08:46.480 --> 08:48.440
If there are clues
about the murder weapon,

08:48.440 --> 08:49.840
it would be very helpful.

08:50.160 --> 08:51.400
Then... What is that?

08:52.080 --> 08:53.880
It should have a certain weight.

08:54.490 --> 08:57.870
It might have a curved shape.

08:58.200 --> 09:01.380
This is a gift Yuan gave to Xiao Su.

09:02.240 --> 09:03.600
He liked it the most

09:04.240 --> 09:05.970
and always carried it with him.

09:06.710 --> 09:08.770
[NO SMOKING]

09:08.160 --> 09:08.960
Officers,

09:08.770 --> 09:12.210
[Upstairs]

09:09.360 --> 09:11.490
a lady just asked me to give this to you.

09:24.850 --> 09:25.150
[July 22, 2019]

09:27.380 --> 09:28.710
[July 22, 2019]

09:35.390 --> 09:37.120
No biological

09:37.120 --> 09:38.200
DNA samples were detected on this.

09:37.780 --> 09:38.430
[Sample No. 1 submitted for examination
yielded no findings.]

09:38.450 --> 09:39.260
[STR classification: No DNA remains]

09:39.200 --> 09:40.060
Keep this safe.

09:59.750 --> 10:03.150
This is the only thing your sister
left you to remember her by.

10:04.600 --> 10:06.800
Actually, you don't have to destroy it.

10:07.550 --> 10:10.280
Officer Li and the others
have already tested it.

10:10.390 --> 10:12.510
There's no DNA residue on it.

10:22.550 --> 10:23.750
When did it start?

10:26.320 --> 10:27.600
When my mom met you?

10:30.550 --> 10:30.910
No,

10:32.390 --> 10:33.190
even earlier.

10:35.720 --> 10:37.440
When Officer Li called you,

10:38.960 --> 10:40.560
you completely betrayed me.

10:41.750 --> 10:42.720
Why me?

10:45.510 --> 10:46.570
Because I love you.

10:47.840 --> 10:48.240
Love?

10:52.910 --> 10:54.640
Just like how you loved He Xiao,

10:55.480 --> 10:56.440
Xie Ke,

10:57.670 --> 10:58.630
Wei Zhihua,

10:59.030 --> 11:00.150
and Qiao Zishan?

11:10.550 --> 11:12.080
How can they compare to you?

11:14.290 --> 11:15.400
You are my wife.

11:17.630 --> 11:20.490
We are going to spend
the rest of our lives together.

11:20.790 --> 11:21.480
Are we?

11:25.840 --> 11:28.440
You've probably said
these things to them too.

11:29.790 --> 11:31.240
He Xiao funded you

11:31.750 --> 11:34.150
to go to Harbor Island
for graduate school.

11:34.510 --> 11:36.370
She abandoned her family for you.

11:38.600 --> 11:40.120
I've told you this before.

11:42.200 --> 11:43.800
It was her wishful thinking.

11:46.630 --> 11:47.360
Was it?

11:48.440 --> 11:49.790
Wasn't it because you

11:50.360 --> 11:51.890
wanted her family's money,

11:52.440 --> 11:54.120
and seeing how close she was to her son

11:54.120 --> 11:55.120
made you jealous,

11:55.320 --> 11:56.920
so you wanted to destroy her?

11:59.150 --> 12:00.810
Your imagination is too wild.

12:03.120 --> 12:04.840
And the Ice Queen, Xie Ke.

12:05.910 --> 12:06.960
Did you choose her

12:08.240 --> 12:09.000
to enjoy the thrill

12:09.000 --> 12:11.120
of crushing her under your feet?

12:13.840 --> 12:14.670
Qiao Zishan

12:15.720 --> 12:17.140
had a bright future ahead of her

12:17.140 --> 12:19.000
and she was about to study abroad.

12:19.240 --> 12:20.610
Why did you destroy her?

12:21.960 --> 12:23.620
Was it because her appearance

12:23.910 --> 12:25.710
reminded you of your first love?

12:29.550 --> 12:30.360
Are you done?

12:33.470 --> 12:34.720
Is all this nonsense

12:35.720 --> 12:37.720
something that Officer Li told you?

12:40.600 --> 12:41.150
Yan Ling,

12:43.100 --> 12:44.900
you are a university professor.

12:45.600 --> 12:47.350
At least use your brain.

12:48.320 --> 12:49.720
Just like how you look down
on Li Changning

12:49.720 --> 12:51.180
for being so love-struck.

12:51.600 --> 12:52.600
They are the same,

12:54.000 --> 12:55.060
weak and ignorant.

12:56.000 --> 12:57.720
They chose their own fate.

12:58.440 --> 13:00.100
What does it have to do with me?

13:01.840 --> 13:04.100
Then when I am driven to
a dead end one day,

13:05.440 --> 13:07.440
will you also tell everyone

13:07.790 --> 13:09.390
it was my own choice

13:09.390 --> 13:11.450
and that it has nothing to do with you?

13:12.030 --> 13:13.230
They are just like me.

13:13.600 --> 13:14.630
Out of trust,

13:16.200 --> 13:18.660
we exposed our wounds
and weaknesses to you.

13:20.030 --> 13:20.970
But you

13:21.960 --> 13:23.020
turned all of these

13:23.270 --> 13:25.080
into knives stabbing us.

13:26.790 --> 13:28.950
You keep saying that we are the same,

13:29.350 --> 13:31.080
that we are gifts to each other.

13:31.840 --> 13:33.100
Actually, you chose me

13:34.360 --> 13:36.970
just because I am a wounded prey,

13:37.120 --> 13:39.250
which is easier for you to manipulate—

13:39.360 --> 13:41.020
like a lion picking a gazelle,

13:42.440 --> 13:44.500
always going for the one that's hurt.

13:45.270 --> 13:46.270
Isn't that right?

13:53.030 --> 13:54.830
You really haven't grown at all.

13:55.790 --> 13:57.850
You're still acting like the victim.

13:58.930 --> 14:01.590
You think all the mistakes
were caused by others

14:02.000 --> 14:04.260
and that they have nothing to do with you.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.480
I am not a lion,

14:06.320 --> 14:07.850
and you are not an antelope.

14:08.240 --> 14:09.670
No antelope is like you.

14:12.600 --> 14:13.670
You stole my keys

14:14.790 --> 14:15.870
and entered my room

14:15.870 --> 14:17.200
without my permission,

14:17.790 --> 14:20.120
guarding against your lover like a thief.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.670
Don't pin this on me.

14:24.240 --> 14:25.840
You're just feeling guilty.

14:26.550 --> 14:29.280
If you wanted to destroy
that pen holder so badly,

14:29.510 --> 14:31.390
why didn't you just take it away from home

14:31.390 --> 14:32.390
and throw it away?

14:35.840 --> 14:38.360
You know this is our home.

14:39.720 --> 14:41.710
It's a home for you and me.

14:43.120 --> 14:44.970
It's the warmest

14:45.150 --> 14:46.510
and safest place for me.

14:47.390 --> 14:49.320
Why did you have to ruin it?

14:50.200 --> 14:50.670
Why?

14:51.960 --> 14:53.760
You've really disappointed me.

14:54.860 --> 14:55.990
I used to think that,

14:56.030 --> 14:57.150
in this world,

14:57.840 --> 14:59.370
at least you understood me.

14:59.720 --> 15:00.320
I don't.

15:02.240 --> 15:04.630
I don't understand
where your hatred comes from—

15:04.630 --> 15:06.360
treating all women as enemies,

15:08.390 --> 15:10.440
not even sparing your own sister.

15:16.040 --> 15:16.970
What did you say?

15:19.440 --> 15:21.680
That Wei Zhihua who worked at the salon—

15:22.590 --> 15:24.790
you called her "Edward Scissorhands."

15:25.360 --> 15:26.390
Did you kill her

15:27.900 --> 15:29.500
because her existence

15:29.630 --> 15:31.670
constantly reminded you

15:32.110 --> 15:34.790
of the vile thoughts
you once had about your own sister—

15:34.790 --> 15:36.390
thoughts lower than a beast?

15:38.420 --> 15:39.610
Nonsense!

15:40.030 --> 15:42.990
I didn't. She is my sister.

15:43.680 --> 15:45.150
I never had any of those

15:45.150 --> 15:46.720
disgusting, filthy thoughts about her.

15:46.720 --> 15:47.910
I know you didn't.

15:48.990 --> 15:50.800
But this is your PUA trick

15:51.630 --> 15:54.950
to suppress
and humiliate others, isn't it?

16:02.900 --> 16:05.900
I know you only have family affection
for your sister.

16:06.630 --> 16:07.690
But how does it feel

16:08.600 --> 16:10.680
to be humiliated and misinterpreted?

16:10.680 --> 16:11.520
Does it hurt?

16:12.870 --> 16:15.260
Just like when you knew
I hated Ding Zhibo,

16:15.560 --> 16:16.990
but you said I loved him,

16:17.160 --> 16:19.160
leaving me unable to defend myself.

16:19.370 --> 16:21.880
So you used this set of PUA tricks,

16:21.920 --> 16:23.450
watching the women who love

16:23.510 --> 16:25.850
and trust you crumble in front of you,

16:26.110 --> 16:27.630
thinking you're clever

16:27.660 --> 16:28.560
and smart.

16:29.260 --> 16:30.060
You're wrong.

16:31.630 --> 16:32.960
You being able to hurt us

16:33.970 --> 16:35.500
doesn't mean you're smart.

16:37.940 --> 16:40.000
It's because you have no bottom line.

16:41.170 --> 16:42.360
You have no heart.

16:43.640 --> 16:44.810
I have no heart?

16:46.480 --> 16:48.040
If I didn't care about you,

16:48.850 --> 16:51.280
how could you ever hurt me like this?

16:56.120 --> 16:57.490
I really do love you.

16:59.730 --> 17:01.060
I don't want to lose you.

17:03.190 --> 17:05.859
I don't want you
to leave me like my sister did.

17:09.940 --> 17:11.650
What have you done

17:13.520 --> 17:15.450
for your so-called "not leaving"?

17:17.800 --> 17:18.760
Officer Li

17:20.050 --> 17:23.109
found the old policeman
who handled the case back then.

17:25.900 --> 17:27.900
He said the one who called the police

17:29.460 --> 17:31.790
to report your sister for drug possession

17:33.590 --> 17:35.170
was a kid.

17:38.590 --> 17:39.480
Sister...

17:39.600 --> 17:48.780
[Public phone]

17:41.350 --> 17:44.770
Sister, take me with you.

17:51.400 --> 17:52.550
Study hard.

17:53.720 --> 17:55.050
I will come back for you.

17:58.180 --> 18:03.790
[Public phone]

18:02.270 --> 18:02.960
Sister.

18:30.510 --> 18:31.910
I want to call the police.

18:31.920 --> 18:34.740
Jian, no, Chen Lijian is taking drugs.

18:35.000 --> 18:37.200
He also wants to run away with Xiao Yuan.

19:10.690 --> 19:12.420
-Freeze!
-Police! Freeze!

19:12.510 --> 19:13.100
Get down!

19:14.350 --> 19:15.010
Don't move!

19:15.030 --> 19:16.960
Who told you to grab my instrument?

19:17.630 --> 19:18.230
Get down!

19:18.480 --> 19:19.140
Don't move!

19:38.240 --> 19:38.970
Does it hurt?

19:41.830 --> 19:42.490
No.

19:47.160 --> 19:48.490
Since I've been gone,

19:50.400 --> 19:51.400
you've suffered.

19:54.110 --> 19:54.720
I haven't.

20:01.200 --> 20:02.660
I promise to take you away.

20:03.200 --> 20:05.130
I won't let you get beaten anymore.

20:07.000 --> 20:08.600
Will you really take me away?

20:14.750 --> 20:16.000
Jian has two more years

20:16.000 --> 20:17.670
to serve in Ningxia.

20:18.310 --> 20:20.850
I'm planning to open a hair salon there

20:20.880 --> 20:22.140
called "Yuan's Salon"

20:22.750 --> 20:25.550
so I can earn money
while waiting for him to get out.

20:25.920 --> 20:28.780
Then we can go together to Harbor Island

20:28.920 --> 20:31.490
to watch a concert at Hongkan Stadium.

20:33.920 --> 20:34.380
Sister,

20:36.110 --> 20:37.770
take me with you to make money.

20:37.920 --> 20:39.240
You can't make money.

20:41.160 --> 20:42.300
You must study hard.

20:42.510 --> 20:43.920
You are the smartest in the family.

20:43.920 --> 20:45.420
I am really studying hard.

20:47.110 --> 20:47.710
Really.

20:48.680 --> 20:50.940
I know you've got this kind of potential.

20:51.310 --> 20:52.270
For the rest of my life,

20:52.270 --> 20:54.030
I can only do haircuts for others.

20:54.030 --> 20:55.090
You are different.

20:55.310 --> 20:58.070
You're going to be a PhD, a doctor,

20:59.720 --> 21:00.850
wielding a scalpel.

21:01.350 --> 21:03.880
You've always been
so skillful with your hands.

21:03.880 --> 21:06.080
You're going to the best universities,

21:06.510 --> 21:08.710
maybe Shenchuan, maybe Harbor Island,

21:09.030 --> 21:10.890
and I'll work to pay your tuition.

21:12.270 --> 21:12.810
No.

21:13.640 --> 21:15.110
I just had a dream.

21:19.070 --> 21:19.720
Yuan!

21:20.270 --> 21:20.970
Yuan!

21:21.160 --> 21:21.860
Sister!

21:22.310 --> 21:23.000
Sister!

21:23.480 --> 21:24.550
I'm never coming back

21:24.550 --> 21:26.520
to this house again.

21:26.750 --> 21:29.060
Sister, wait for me!

21:30.160 --> 21:30.880
Sister,

21:31.270 --> 21:32.630
take me with you!

21:32.720 --> 21:33.550
Sister!

21:35.270 --> 21:36.030
Sister!

21:38.200 --> 21:39.030
Sister!

21:41.070 --> 21:41.670
Sister!

21:43.640 --> 21:44.380
Sister!

21:45.750 --> 21:46.400
Sister!

21:49.640 --> 21:50.400
Sister,

21:50.920 --> 21:52.000
where are you?

21:53.240 --> 21:54.030
Sister!

21:55.590 --> 21:56.200
Sister!

21:58.440 --> 21:59.040
Sister!

22:00.960 --> 22:01.550
Sister!

22:02.550 --> 22:03.020
Sister!

22:03.680 --> 22:04.070
Help me!

22:04.070 --> 22:04.530
Sister!

22:04.790 --> 22:06.390
-Sister, I'm here.
-Help me!

22:06.720 --> 22:07.180
Sister!

22:08.240 --> 22:08.920
Su, help me!

22:11.240 --> 22:11.850
Sister!

22:11.950 --> 22:13.220
Sister, grab me!

22:13.790 --> 22:14.790
-Here!
-Help me!

22:14.790 --> 22:15.720
Grab me, sister.

22:16.550 --> 22:17.060
Sister.

22:17.830 --> 22:18.330
Help me.

22:18.400 --> 22:18.990
Sister.

22:20.880 --> 22:21.340
Sister.

22:22.070 --> 22:22.870
Hold on tight.

22:22.880 --> 22:24.270
Don't let go.

22:24.350 --> 22:25.560
-Let me help you up.
-Help me!

22:25.560 --> 22:26.020
Sister!

22:29.680 --> 22:31.680
-Su, help me up.
-Sister.

22:31.720 --> 22:32.180
Sister,

22:32.720 --> 22:34.250
you have to take me with you.

22:34.510 --> 22:35.030
Believe me,

22:35.030 --> 22:36.350
I really didn't do anything.

22:36.350 --> 22:37.880
I'm not that kind of person.

22:38.110 --> 22:38.790
Hold on to me.

22:38.790 --> 22:40.000
Help me, Su.

22:40.680 --> 22:41.510
Su.

22:43.510 --> 22:44.240
Yuan!

22:46.240 --> 22:47.130
Grab me.

22:47.180 --> 22:48.020
Don't let go.

22:51.680 --> 22:53.500
Jian? Chen Lijian.

22:53.550 --> 22:55.330
[Jian]

22:56.570 --> 22:58.570
You never wanted to take me with you.

22:58.640 --> 23:00.300
You only have him in your heart.

23:00.300 --> 23:01.960
You don't care about me at all.

23:02.770 --> 23:03.640
You lied to me.

23:04.350 --> 23:04.830
No!

23:04.830 --> 23:05.610
You're lying.

23:05.610 --> 23:06.040
Su,

23:06.300 --> 23:06.960
no.

23:07.590 --> 23:07.880
Su.

23:07.880 --> 23:10.080
You only have Chen Lijian in your heart.

23:10.590 --> 23:12.250
You don't care about me at all.

23:12.270 --> 23:13.080
Su.

23:13.200 --> 23:14.030
You liar.

23:14.050 --> 23:16.050
-I didn't.
-You've been lying to me.

23:16.200 --> 23:17.470
It's all your fault.

23:18.480 --> 23:19.240
Your fault.

23:19.830 --> 23:21.290
It's all your fault.

23:22.680 --> 23:23.620
Liar.

23:28.350 --> 23:29.770
You lied to me first.

23:30.160 --> 23:30.640
Help me!

23:31.440 --> 23:33.120
You lied first.

23:37.960 --> 23:40.360
You never really
wanted to take me with you.

23:41.110 --> 23:41.820
Su!

23:49.310 --> 23:50.550
Why didn't you do

23:52.440 --> 23:54.080
what you promised me?

23:58.050 --> 23:59.180
It's all your fault.

23:59.360 --> 24:01.600
It's your fault. Your fault.

24:03.090 --> 24:05.470
It's not my fault. Don't blame me.

24:13.840 --> 24:15.120
Su!

24:41.240 --> 24:43.480
Why didn't you do what you promised me?

24:45.470 --> 24:46.400
It was her fault.

24:49.640 --> 24:50.920
She lied to me first.

24:52.680 --> 24:54.410
Why didn't you take me with you?

24:55.310 --> 24:57.570
She left me to suffer in that house alone.

25:04.030 --> 25:05.240
You are all the same.

25:07.510 --> 25:09.030
None of you truly love me.

25:11.680 --> 25:13.070
You all want to hurt me.

25:25.670 --> 25:26.430
It hurts.

25:30.210 --> 25:31.590
It really hurts.

25:47.270 --> 25:48.920
I grew up being beaten.

25:53.000 --> 25:54.240
I'm so scared.

25:57.270 --> 25:58.680
I'm terrified of pain.

26:02.680 --> 26:04.830
I don't like people hurting me.

26:08.030 --> 26:10.790
That's why I grew thorns
to protect myself.

26:13.640 --> 26:15.550
I hurt people

26:15.580 --> 26:17.040
before they could hurt me.

26:18.840 --> 26:20.100
Can you understand me?

26:22.830 --> 26:24.510
You and I are the same.

26:25.440 --> 26:28.500
We both lost the family members
we least wanted to lose.

26:29.270 --> 26:30.400
We are both suffering

26:30.400 --> 26:32.680
torture that others cannot imagine.

26:37.350 --> 26:38.810
We've both made mistakes.

26:40.880 --> 26:42.350
We've both been wronged.

26:45.110 --> 26:46.640
You should understand me.

26:47.720 --> 26:49.450
It was because I met you

26:49.680 --> 26:50.540
that I realized

26:50.920 --> 26:53.570
there was someone like me in this world.

26:54.510 --> 26:57.410
You gave me the hope to start over.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.110
Honey,

27:02.590 --> 27:04.480
could you please teach me?

27:05.920 --> 27:07.210
Teach me.

27:07.830 --> 27:09.030
I don't know love.

27:10.790 --> 27:12.590
I don't know how to love.

27:14.030 --> 27:15.720
I didn't mean to hurt you.

27:17.400 --> 27:19.110
Don't leave me.

27:21.510 --> 27:22.920
Don't leave me.

27:28.920 --> 27:30.880
I never thought of leaving you.

27:34.270 --> 27:36.310
I gave you my all.

27:37.720 --> 27:40.050
I gave you
the most unbearable parts of me.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.000
My love for you

27:45.530 --> 27:47.310
is no less than yours.

27:49.920 --> 27:51.790
What do you want me to do to feel it?

28:04.000 --> 28:05.450
Give me another chance.

28:08.110 --> 28:09.440
Don't give up on me.

28:11.590 --> 28:14.440
Let's leave
all those broken pieces behind.

28:16.400 --> 28:19.510
Let's pretend
it never happened in our lives.

28:20.440 --> 28:21.970
From now on, just you and me.

28:23.270 --> 28:24.920
Shall we start over?

28:26.600 --> 28:28.000
Let's start over.

28:30.510 --> 28:31.640
Yan Ling, I love you.

28:32.920 --> 28:33.860
Don't leave me.

28:37.400 --> 28:38.440
Don't leave me.

28:53.720 --> 28:55.590
You said you'd rather hurt others

28:57.820 --> 28:59.620
than let others hurt you.

29:02.920 --> 29:04.920
Then why didn't you hurt

29:06.590 --> 29:07.750
your first love—

29:08.350 --> 29:09.480
Xu Jingyun?

29:15.720 --> 29:17.240
She cut your hand

29:18.790 --> 29:20.440
and ruined your future.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.590
She can make you hide

29:25.590 --> 29:26.880
under someone else's identity

29:26.880 --> 29:29.480
for the rest of your life,
never seeing the light of day.

29:29.480 --> 29:31.810
But you didn't dare
get close to her again.

29:35.790 --> 29:36.870
Because you know

29:37.680 --> 29:38.920
she and her family

29:41.000 --> 29:43.070
could destroy you at any moment,

29:46.590 --> 29:48.900
as easily as crushing an ant.

29:52.110 --> 29:53.480
So you were scared.

29:56.680 --> 29:59.440
You only dared to
target ordinary women like us,

30:01.310 --> 30:03.440
venting all your resentment

30:05.110 --> 30:07.060
and dissatisfaction on us.

30:10.030 --> 30:13.430
You're just a clown
who bullies the weak and fears the strong.

31:00.880 --> 31:02.680
When you were speaking just now,

31:04.880 --> 31:06.140
you were so beautiful.

31:07.640 --> 31:09.900
I really didn't choose the wrong person.

31:10.590 --> 31:12.120
You really are the smartest

31:12.900 --> 31:13.830
and know me best.

31:18.610 --> 31:19.640
But why bother?

31:23.110 --> 31:24.440
You ruined your father,

31:25.270 --> 31:26.070
your mother,

31:26.790 --> 31:27.960
and yourself.

31:30.160 --> 31:31.880
Are you going to ruin me now?

31:32.720 --> 31:33.920
No one can ruin you.

31:35.320 --> 31:36.920
Just like you said yourself,

31:38.400 --> 31:39.590
everyone's fate

31:40.920 --> 31:42.110
is their own choice.

31:44.790 --> 31:46.250
Just like that pen holder—

31:47.550 --> 31:49.510
it could have just stayed there

31:50.790 --> 31:52.000
quietly and safely.

32:03.270 --> 32:05.070
But you knew there were cameras.

32:06.420 --> 32:07.990
No normal person

32:09.070 --> 32:12.130
would install 8 surveillance cameras
in their own home

32:12.720 --> 32:14.650
unless they were a little twisted.

32:16.000 --> 32:16.890
Lu said

32:18.510 --> 32:21.440
you would definitely
leave a safe zone for yourself,

32:22.110 --> 32:25.040
so that no one would
find out if you did something bad.

32:26.110 --> 32:26.750
So,

32:29.000 --> 32:30.660
I also learned to install one.

32:34.680 --> 32:35.410
Right there.

32:38.920 --> 32:40.350
I recorded

32:42.480 --> 32:43.810
everything bad you did.

33:00.370 --> 33:05.130
[Friday, July 26, 2019]

33:09.480 --> 33:11.700
[Friday, July 26, 2019]

33:15.230 --> 33:16.520
[Police]

33:29.400 --> 33:31.040
It's all over, Luo Liang.

33:32.110 --> 33:35.290
You have to pay for your mistakes.

33:39.600 --> 33:40.350
You two stay here.

33:40.350 --> 33:41.950
The rest of you, come with me.

33:42.590 --> 33:43.480
Go, go, go!

33:47.070 --> 33:48.080
You're so stupid.

33:49.210 --> 33:50.780
You don't know

33:51.550 --> 33:53.140
how much I love you.

33:55.770 --> 33:56.830
Do you even realize

33:59.360 --> 34:00.900
how much I've done

34:02.110 --> 34:04.980
to protect our home
for the sake of loving you?

34:06.410 --> 34:07.850
Did you know

34:09.610 --> 34:10.800
how much water

34:12.320 --> 34:13.820
your mother drank,

34:15.080 --> 34:17.280
and how much she suffered when she died?

34:17.400 --> 34:18.330
What did you say?

34:28.020 --> 34:29.429
I can't let her live.

34:31.070 --> 34:33.260
She will destroy our relationship.

34:34.550 --> 34:36.010
So she had to die—

34:38.929 --> 34:40.230
just like my sister,

34:41.489 --> 34:43.199
falling into the water alive,

34:45.480 --> 34:46.920
gulping it down,

34:50.110 --> 34:50.800
finally,

34:51.510 --> 34:53.270
unable to get even a breath…

34:54.320 --> 34:55.320
Just like that,

34:55.870 --> 34:56.810
slowly,

34:58.070 --> 34:59.030
slowly,

35:01.360 --> 35:02.190
suffocating,

35:03.960 --> 35:05.050
and dying.

35:13.880 --> 35:14.550
Kill me!

35:14.710 --> 35:15.190
Come on!

35:15.810 --> 35:16.990
You are just like me.

35:17.360 --> 35:18.680
Avenge your mom.

35:21.030 --> 35:21.590
Come on!

35:23.970 --> 35:24.540
Sister!

35:24.880 --> 35:25.510
Yan Ling!

35:29.730 --> 35:31.400
I won't let you ruin me.

35:32.750 --> 35:34.230
You'll never forget me.

35:56.370 --> 35:57.860
[Six months later]

35:58.840 --> 36:00.630
When I was little, my dad told me

36:01.770 --> 36:03.290
that while he was at sea,

36:03.860 --> 36:05.790
he encountered a humpback whale.

36:06.930 --> 36:09.190
It was attacked by a pod of killer whales.

36:09.630 --> 36:11.820
It struggled for over 4 hours,

36:12.230 --> 36:14.250
and eventually lost its dorsal fin.

36:16.550 --> 36:20.920
The crew said its blood
would attract predators,

36:21.440 --> 36:23.830
the wound would get infected by seawater,

36:23.880 --> 36:25.940
and it definitely wouldn't survive.

36:29.280 --> 36:30.540
Sometimes I feel

36:31.460 --> 36:33.640
like I am that humpback whale.

36:34.190 --> 36:35.630
The wound hasn't healed,

36:36.840 --> 36:39.960
and the smell of blood
attracts new hunters.

36:40.460 --> 36:42.190
