[Enhancing Self-Awareness]

36:43.470 --> 36:45.890
You might be wondering

36:44.170 --> 36:45.400
[Techniques to
Identify Emotional Manipulation]
[Case Studies and Discussions]

36:45.400 --> 36:47.470
[Saying No to PUA]

36:46.510 --> 36:47.740
how I healed

36:48.380 --> 36:49.650
from such deep wounds.

36:51.770 --> 36:53.260
The truth is, even today,

36:55.130 --> 36:56.610
I still feel the pain.

36:58.450 --> 37:00.430
I still wake up from nightmares.

37:02.750 --> 37:04.430
I even worry

37:05.230 --> 37:06.290
whether this wound

37:06.960 --> 37:08.590
will ever fully heal?

37:13.300 --> 37:14.990
But I am still alive,

37:17.190 --> 37:19.780
which means this wound isn't fatal.

37:20.880 --> 37:25.140
What's truly fatal is surrendering to it.

37:26.280 --> 37:28.940
Just like the story
I haven't finished telling.

37:29.760 --> 37:30.760
Five years later,

37:31.230 --> 37:34.400
my father and the others returned to
that same stretch of sea.

37:34.400 --> 37:35.720
They rescued a

37:35.840 --> 37:39.300
baby whale that had almost been shredded
by a ship's propeller

37:40.000 --> 37:41.600
and soon its mother arrived,

37:45.240 --> 37:47.500
a humpback whale missing its dorsal fin,

37:48.670 --> 37:51.170
yet still swimming freely in the ocean.

37:54.230 --> 37:55.880
The scar on her back

37:57.070 --> 37:59.250
looked like a warrior's medal.

38:04.270 --> 38:06.070
I believe that each of you here today

38:06.070 --> 38:07.200
carries deep wounds

38:08.350 --> 38:09.410
in your own hearts,

38:10.110 --> 38:11.850
just like I do.

38:13.030 --> 38:14.640
But the fact

38:15.610 --> 38:17.010
that we are here together

38:17.150 --> 38:18.960
shows that we no longer see

38:20.960 --> 38:23.030
those wounds as a shame to hide.

38:24.030 --> 38:25.180
It shows that we are

38:26.030 --> 38:27.470
facing them

38:28.030 --> 38:29.360
and crossing over them.

38:30.100 --> 38:35.250
[Defendant]

38:32.220 --> 38:34.870
Those who once gave us wounds

38:35.630 --> 38:37.110
are no stronger than us.

38:37.840 --> 38:40.120
They only hide

38:40.140 --> 38:41.870
behind lies and performances,

38:42.190 --> 38:43.550
never daring

38:43.570 --> 38:46.210
to reveal their true selves in the light.

38:48.070 --> 38:48.880
I believe

38:49.590 --> 38:53.440
their crimes will be punished by the law.

38:58.430 --> 39:00.690
And just like that brave humpback whale,

39:02.630 --> 39:05.630
we can live and love,

39:06.480 --> 39:07.880
even carrying our scars,

39:11.030 --> 39:12.200
because we know

39:12.970 --> 39:14.780
what grows out of those wounds

39:15.710 --> 39:18.800
will definitely be stronger muscles.

39:30.310 --> 39:31.970
Your mom is great, isn't she?

39:33.510 --> 39:34.530
But

39:34.550 --> 39:37.150
I didn't quite understand
what she was saying.

