41:02.260 --> 41:03.170
Dad, Mom.

41:03.800 --> 41:06.190
Jiale and I are doing pretty well now.

41:08.000 --> 41:09.800
I'm better than ever before.

41:10.740 --> 41:11.660
Don't worry.

41:27.220 --> 41:27.900
[According to
the Criminal Law of the People's Republic of China,]

41:27.930 --> 41:28.600
[Article 260,]

41:28.620 --> 41:29.430
[and the Anti-Domestic Violence Law,]

41:29.450 --> 41:30.200
[Article 2, abuse and domestic violence]

41:30.230 --> 41:31.180
[include not only physical abuse]

41:31.200 --> 41:32.170
[but also psychological torment.]

41:32.200 --> 41:33.300
[Sustained and frequent
emotional abuse is also]

41:33.330 --> 41:34.180
[a crime. Related personnel
in the Xiao Su case,]

41:34.210 --> 41:35.460
[Xu Feng and others,
have all been legally punished.]

